Class Movie

  • java.lang.Object
    • Movie

  • public class Movie
extends java.lang.Object
    Movie object tracks an movie, its Rotten Tomatoes rating, and the actors appearing in the movie.
    Author:
    kjnorris

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructor and Description
      Movie(java.lang.String name)
